# Cryptographic Registry

All capabilities must be registered with their corresponding input/output schemas and cryptographic verification keys.

```json
{
  "registry_version": "2026.05.20.001",
  "jurisdiction": "global",
  "constitution_version": "v4.02.1",
  "capabilities": [
    {
      "id": "cap-abide-intent-compiler",
      "schema_hash": "sha256:9f8e7d6c5b4a3f2e1d0c9b8a7f6e5d4c3b2a1f0e9d8c7b6a5f4e3d2c1b0a9f8e",
      "verification_key": "ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAI..."
    }
  ]
}
```
